---
title: Honey Haloumi & Roast Veggie Salad with Garlic Aioli & Flaked Almonds
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful Mediterranean haloumi meets roasted vegetables tossed with mild spices, and there’s a tangy aioli and toasted almonds to finish it off.
